{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_YY03_100.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x20,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "...Um, there's something that I need to talk to you about, Plachta."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "With me? What is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "...I'm thinking about going on a journey, to take the official alchemist license exam."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "License exam... Do you mean the one that Julio mentioned?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. Apparently, my grandma took that exam, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "...I see. If I recall, you started alchemy because of your grandmother."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yup. That's why... I want to go and take the exam too, to follow in her footsteps."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "...What do you think?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I don't think that matters... This is something you decided, I wouldn't object."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "If you wish to do it, then go right ahead. You have my support."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Plachta...! Yeah, thanks!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "...Also. I'm not just thinking about going on a journey for the exam."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "What other goal do you have?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Well... You know how I asked you before? About materials that can't be found in this region."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Those materials... Are to give you a human body, Plachta."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xf,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "...! What do you mean by that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "You don't taste anything when you eat food. That was always something that bothered me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "And I'm sure you sense things besides taste differently from me, too..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "That's probably because you have a doll's body... Because I couldn't give you a real human body."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "...This might sound selfish, but I want you to see things the same way as I do. To feel the same way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "That's why... I know I gave up once, but I want to give you a human body, Plachta."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "...I'd be going on a journey to gather materials for that, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Hm... You really, really are soft hearted, to a hopeless extent."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x6b,
            "expr_id": 0xc,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "...Thank you. To think you'd have so much consideration for me... I really am happy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I'd like to ask one thing... Do you mind if I accompany you on your journey?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Of course it's fine! Besides, I'd be too lonely without you around..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "...Then let us set out on a journey together. I'll always follow you, no matter where you go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "...At least, as long as I draw breath, so to speak."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Yeah! I'll be together with you forever too, Plachta!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x45,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Okay then... I need to make preparations, so we can set out."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x47,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "I'll think of things we need for the journey."
        }
    ]
}